Welcome to Meat with the Press, a new video series where Dallas Morning News reporter Evan Grant — known for both his baseball and barbecue acumen — takes notable North Texans out for a conversation over good food.
The first episode features Rangers slugger Joey Gallo at Zoli’s NY Pizza in Addison.
Evan and Joey talk all things food (including Joey’s affinity for his mom’s meatballs), baseball and life in general.
